'''Kabul Rock''', 108.0 FM is a rock station in [[Kabul]], Afghanistan, playing music ranging from 1950s' [[rockabilly]] to modern [[Rock music|rock]] and [[Heavy metal music|metal]].

==Range==
Its base stations have been attacked and threatened by [[insurgent]]s, and thus are very well hidden and not known to many.  It can be heard within greater Kabul and most of the way to [[Bagram]], where the signal fades.  

